ðŸ“ DAX Measures

1ï¸âƒ£ Rooms Sold

Rooms Sold = SUM ( Bookings[Rooms Booked] )

2ï¸âƒ£ Rooms Available

Rooms Available = SUM ( Hotels[Total Rooms] )

3ï¸âƒ£ Occupancy %

Occupancy % = DIVIDE ( [Rooms Sold], [Rooms Available], 0 )

4ï¸âƒ£ Total Revenue

Total Revenue = SUM ( Bookings[Revenue] )

5ï¸âƒ£ Average Daily Rate (ADR)

ADR = DIVIDE ( [Total Revenue], [Rooms Sold], 0 )

6ï¸âƒ£ Revenue per Available Room (RevPAR)

RevPAR = DIVIDE ( [Total Revenue], [Rooms Available], 0 )

DAX Measures

Direct Revenue = CALCULATE ( [Total Revenue], Bookings[Booking Source] = "Direct" )

OTA Revenue = CALCULATE ( [Total Revenue], Bookings[Booking Source] = "OTA"

ðŸŽ›ï¸ Interactive Slicers

Implemented slicers for:

Room Type

Hotel Branch / Location

Booking Source

Date Range

All slicers interact dynamically with all visuals.

ðŸ‘¥ Guest Classification Metrics

Guest Measures

Total Bookings per Guest = COUNT ( Bookings[Booking_ID] )

Total Spend per Guest = SUM ( Bookings[Revenue] )

Guest Segmentation Column

Guest Segment = SWITCH ( TRUE(), [Total Spend per Guest] >= 50000, "High Spender", [Total Bookings per Guest] >= 3, "Loyal Guest", [Total Bookings per Guest] = 1, "First-time Guest", "Regular Guest" )

